1
00:00:09,480 --> 00:00:10,843
A moment's reflection.

2
00:00:10,864 --> 00:00:30,544
A resolution.

3
00:00:45,779 --> 00:00:48,154
And we can take the refuges and precepts.

4
00:00:50,527 --> 00:00:52,902
So feel free to make three bows.

5
00:01:19,596 --> 00:01:43,748
Namo tassa bhagavato harahato sambha sambuddhasa Namo tassa bhagavato harahato sambha sambuddhasa

6
00:01:51,996 --> 00:02:00,608
Namo tassa bhagavato hara-hatto sambha-sambhodassa.

7
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:13,768
Bodhamsaranam gacchami.

8
00:02:18,997 --> 00:02:45,966
Dhamam saranam gacchami Sangam saranam gacchami Dutiyampi buddham saranam gacchami

9
00:02:52,460 --> 00:03:12,848
Duthi Ampe Dhamam Saranam Gacchami Duthi Ampe Sangam Saranam Gacchami

10
00:03:20,556 --> 00:03:41,855
Thati Ampi Bodham Sarnam Gacchami Thati Ampi Dhammam Sarnam Gacchami

11
00:03:48,754 --> 00:04:10,998
Tathiyampi Sangam Saranam Gacchami Panati Pata Veramani Sikapadam Samadhi Ami

12
00:04:20,867 --> 00:04:49,187
Adinadana Vairamani Sikapadang Samadhi Ami Kame Sumicacara Vairamani Sikapadang Samadhi Ami

13
00:04:57,351 --> 00:05:05,202
Musa wada veramani sikapadam samadhi amin.

14
00:05:13,935 --> 00:05:25,771
Sura meraya maja pamadhatana veramani sikapadam samadhi amin.

15
00:05:35,810 --> 00:05:52,399
Having taken the refuges and precepts, quoting the last words of the Buddha, let us strive diligently for our liberation.

16
00:05:54,322 --> 00:05:57,649
So now we can practice some metta bhavana, developing goodwill.

17
00:06:07,298 --> 00:06:09,843
May you be safe, well, and happy.

18
00:06:09,882 --> 00:06:14,572
May you live contented in harmony with the world.

19
00:06:15,714 --> 00:06:26,877
We're bringing to mind some of our benefactors.

20
00:06:41,605 --> 00:06:43,954
those who are near and dear to us.

21
00:07:12,553 --> 00:07:15,577
Friends, people at work, whomever we wish.

22
00:07:48,228 --> 00:07:49,750
a neutral person,

23
00:08:15,379 --> 00:08:18,723
turning the stream of goodwill towards ourselves.

24
00:08:46,548 --> 00:08:51,681
And into the heart of goodwill, someone we find difficult or having difficulties with.

25
00:09:19,488 --> 00:09:37,075
Radiating outwards, first of all, to each other, may we.

26
00:09:47,381 --> 00:10:16,225
to our neighbors and neighborhood, to all the people in our country,

27
00:10:43,102 --> 00:10:45,267
to all the peoples of Europe.

28
00:11:13,951 --> 00:11:15,642
to all people on earth.

29
00:11:44,292 --> 00:11:54,251
and to all beings in all directions.

30
00:12:11,528 --> 00:12:16,154
And we can draw the practice to a close with a reading of the Discourse on Loving-Kindness.

31
00:12:17,538 --> 00:12:22,446
If you are wise and want to reach the state of peace, then develop these qualities.

32
00:12:23,326 --> 00:12:27,253
Be upright, responsible, gentle, and unassuming.

33
00:12:28,235 --> 00:12:31,639
Be easily contented and need only a few things.

34
00:12:32,442 --> 00:12:34,585
Be less busy and live simply.

35
00:12:34,644 --> 00:12:38,211
Guard the senses and be modest.

36
00:12:38,883 --> 00:12:42,927
Do not be attached to only a few people, to the exclusion of others.

37
00:12:44,187 --> 00:12:48,030
Do not do the slightest thing that a wise person would blame you for.

38
00:12:49,251 --> 00:12:52,534
And be constantly thinking, may all beings be happy.

39
00:12:53,475 --> 00:13:06,307
Whatever living beings there are, be they weak or strong, big or small, large or slender, living nearby or far away, those who have already been born and those who have yet to be born,

40
00:13:06,980 --> 00:13:09,663
May all beings, without exception, be happy.

41
00:13:11,804 --> 00:13:14,969
Let no one deceive another or disdain anyone.

42
00:13:15,509 --> 00:13:19,113
Do not wish harm to anyone, not even when you're angry.

43
00:13:20,134 --> 00:13:27,481
Just as a mother would protect her only child at the risk of her own life, let the warmth of your heart go out to all beings.

44
00:13:28,143 --> 00:13:36,312
Let your love and goodwill spread throughout the whole world, above and below, without boundary, without ill will or hatred.

45
00:13:37,438 --> 00:13:46,131
Whether you are standing, walking, sitting or lying down, so long as you are awake, develop this affectionate mindfulness.

46
00:13:46,932 --> 00:13:49,176
This, they say, is the noblest way to live.

47
00:13:49,736 --> 00:14:03,817
And if you do not fall into unskillful ways, but live well and develop insight and are no longer attached to all the desires of the senses, then truly you'll never need to be reborn into this world again.

48
00:14:07,139 --> 00:14:35,931
May all beings be happy.

